import { Component } from '@angular/core'; import { AuthService } from '../../services/auth/auth.service'; import { Router } from "@angular/router"; @Component({ selector: 'app-signup-institutions', templateUrl: './signup-institutions.component.html', styleUrls: ['./signup-institutions.component.css'] }) export class SignupInstitutionsComponent { user = { email: '', password: '' }; constructor( private authService: AuthService, private router: Router ) {} signUp() { this.authService.signUp(this.user) .subscribe( (res) => { console.log(res); localStorage.setItem('token', res.token); this.router.navigate(['/list-teachers']); }, (err) => { console.log(err); } ); } }
